			purpose = <"To identifie patients at low, intermediate, and high risk for short-term adverse outcome resulting from acute coronary syndrome (ACS). Based upon five different variables, a score is summed for the patient under evaluation, including history (H), 12-lead electrocardiogram (ECG; E), age (A), risk factors (R), and troponin (T).">
